Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:38.74,ED2-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\1vc(&HF1D056&,&HECCF5E&,&HF3E699&,&HF3E699&)}其實也都無關緊要吧
